        </div>
        <div class="box-card-body">
          <div class="box-card-title">Family Veg Box</div>
          <div class="box-card-meta">6 items · From <strong>$31</strong></div>
          <p class="box-card-desc">A family-size selection of fresh seasonal vegetables — broccoli, carrots, zucchini and more.</p>
          <span class="box-card-cta">See what's inside →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/pages/pantry-saver-bundle" class="box-card">
        <div class="box-card-img">
          <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width=".75" stroke-linecap="round">
            <rect x="4" y="3" width="16" height="18" rx="1.5"/><path d="M4 9h16"/><path d="M4 15h16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="box-card-body">
          <div class="box-card-title">Pantry Saver Bundle</div>
          <div class="box-card-meta">6 items · From <strong>$52</strong></div>
          <p class="box-card-desc">Stock the pantry with everyday staples — rice, oil, pasta and more — at a bundle price.</p>
          <span class="box-card-cta">See what's inside →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/pages/budget-fruit-box" class="box-card">
        <div class="box-card-img">
          <span class="box-card-badge">Budget pick</span>
          <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width=".75" stroke-linecap="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 3c0 0 3 4 3 9s-3 9-3 9"/><path d="M3 12h18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="box-card-body">
          <div class="box-card-title">Budget Fruit Box</div>
          <div class="box-card-meta">4 items · From <strong>$22</strong></div>
          <p class="box-card-desc">Four fruit essentials at a bundle price — always-fresh, family-friendly favourites.</p>
          <span class="box-card-cta">See what's inside →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/pages/full-household-stock-up-box" class="box-card">
        <div class="box-card-img">
          <span class="box-card-badge">Best value</span>
          <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0A4A2F" stroke-width=".75" stroke-linecap="round">
            <path d="M3 9l9-6 9 6v11a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-15A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 20Z"/><path d="M9 21V12h6v9"/>
          </svg>
